name: We2net
additional_notices: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en:
What is the project about?
we2net is a decentralized DeFi project built on the Binance Smart Chain (BSC), dedicated to promoting decentralized finance and providing efficient, transparent, and secure services to global users. We will share with users the permission to add initial liquidity, enabling more people to participate in the decentralized finance market.

What makes your project unique?
Unlike traditional DeFi projects, we have opened up the authority for investors to add initial liquidity, reducing the potential threat that owners may pose to the project. We are also driving the development of the project and community through our unique referral reward mechanism.
History of your project.

What’s next for your project?
The project started development in October last year and underwent countless modifications. It was completed in March this year and passed the security audit by Certik. It was officially launched for sale on April 15th.

What can your token be used for? (Utility, NOT tokenomics)
Rewards can be obtained by staking the early-stage tokens for liquidity, and more attributes will be added based on the development progress of the mobile end in the future.
